{"id":258,"date":"2025-08-29T12:28:15","date_gmt":"2025-08-29T06:58:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp\/?page_id=258"},"modified":"2025-08-31T02:55:06","modified_gmt":"2025-08-30T21:25:06","slug":"photo-gallery","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/photo-gallery\/","title":{"rendered":"Photo gallery"},"content":{"rendered":"        <section class=\"ispl-hero-wrap\" style=\"background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/events-scaled-e1756491795902.jpg');background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/events-scaled-e1756491795902.jpg'); \">\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-overlay\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-inner\" style=\"position:relative; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:6rem 1.25rem;\">\r\n                                    <h2 style=\"font-size:3rem; line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 1rem;\">Moments of Service, Memories of Impact<\/h2>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"font-size:1.125rem; max-width:800px;\">\u201cEvery picture tells a story, and every story reflects the spirit of our service. The Photo Gallery of the Lions Club of Balasore is more than a collection of images\u2014it is a window into the lives we touch, the smiles we share, and the milestones we achieve together. From community projects and health camps to celebrations and fellowship, these photographs capture the heart of our journey\u2014moments where compassion met action and service turned into joy. Each image is a reminder that our work is not measured only in deeds, but in the lasting impressions we leave on people\u2019s hearts. Through these memories, we celebrate our legacy and invite you to witness the change we create, one moment at a time.\u201d<\/p>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"margin-top:2rem;\">\r\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/our-impacts\/\" class=\"ispl-hero-btn\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:.9rem 1.5rem; background:#ffcc00; color:#111; text-decoration:none; border-radius:.35rem; font-weight:600;\">\r\n                            Our Impacts                        <\/a>\r\n                    <\/p>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n        <\/section>\r\n        \n<div class=\"ispl-album-filters\"><button class=\"filter-btn active\" data-album=\"\">All<\/button><button class=\"filter-btn\" data-album=\"default\">Default<\/button><\/div><div id='ispl-gallery-container' class='ispl-gallery-grid' data-masonry='{ \"itemSelector\": \".gallery-item\", \"columnWidth\": \".gallery-sizer\", \"percentPosition\": true }'><div class=\"gallery-sizer\"><\/div><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/gallery\/blanket-distribution\/'><img src='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/PHOTO-2026-06-28-12-37-14-300x225.jpg' alt='Blanket Distribution' \/><\/a><\/div><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/gallery\/picnic\/'><img src='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/PHOTO-2026-06-28-12-36-48_19-300x225.jpg' alt='Picnic' \/><\/a><\/div><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/gallery\/independence-day-celebration-2025\/'><img src='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/PHOTO-2026-06-28-12-36-27_2-300x225.jpg' alt='Independence Day Celebration-2025' \/><\/a><\/div><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/gallery\/mega-free-health-checkup-camp-for-police-personnel\/'><img src='https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/PHOTO-2026-06-28-12-36-08_17-300x225.jpg' alt='Mega free health checkup camp for police personnel' \